                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2001-10-19</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>Rather than just show color combinations in a vacuum, this book uses real examples from different design periods to demonstrate the use of color. Great as both a reference and inspiration. Also just plain nice to look at.</span>
                  
              
